{
  "title": "是鞍山！不是洛杉矶（三）",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "html": "《姨妈的后现代生活》里，其实藏着当年那个特殊年代的<span class=\"vocab\">暗线<span class=\"tooltip\">àn xiàn — hidden thread; underlying plot</span></span>：叶如棠是当年上海女知青，不得已嫁给了当地工人。而在鞍山，和上海有关系的，最有名的就是上海<span class=\"vocab\">老字号<span class=\"tooltip\">lǎo zì hào — time-honored brand</span></span>信利<span class=\"vocab\">熏腊<span class=\"tooltip\">xūn là — Shanghai-style smoked & cured meats shop</span></span>店。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN 3-1.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p3_1.jpg", "alt": "信利熏腊店" }
    },
    {
      "html": "信利<span class=\"vocab\">熏腊<span class=\"tooltip\">xūn là — Shanghai-style smoked & cured meats</span></span>店里卖的都是上海<span class=\"vocab\">江南<span class=\"tooltip\">jiāng nán — Jiangnan region (south of the Yangtze River)</span></span>一带的口味：<span class=\"vocab\">酱鸭<span class=\"tooltip\">jiàng yā — soy-braised duck</span></span>、盐水鸭、<span class=\"vocab\">熏鱼<span class=\"tooltip\">xūn yú — smoked fish</span></span>、<span class=\"vocab\">叉烧肉<span class=\"tooltip\">chā shāo ròu — barbecued pork</span></span>……竟然出现在遥远的东北。原来上世纪五十年代上海也<span class=\"vocab\">派<span class=\"tooltip\">pài — send; assign</span></span>出许多专家支援鞍钢，为了让上海来的专家们适应这儿，政府<span class=\"vocab\">特意<span class=\"tooltip\">tè yì — specially; deliberately</span></span>也把当时上海有名的信利熏腊店整体搬迁到鞍山。<span class=\"vocab\">日久他乡是故乡<span class=\"tooltip\">rì jiǔ tā xiāng shì gù xiāng — over time a foreign land becomes home</span></span>，这些本该是江南口味，成为好几<span class=\"vocab\">代<span class=\"tooltip\">dài — generation; era</span></span>鞍山人的家乡味。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN 3-2.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p3_2.jpg", "alt": "酱鸭与叉烧" }
    },
    {
      "html": "所以说起来，一个国家刚建立，<span class=\"vocab\">百废待兴<span class=\"tooltip\">bǎi fèi dài xīng — all needs to be rebuilt and prosper</span></span>，各地都是互相支援，有的出钢材，有的出木材，有的出食材，有的出人才。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN 3-3.mp4"
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍钢生产<span class=\"vocab\">原料<span class=\"tooltip\">yuán liào — raw material</span></span>主要来自于离市区东边七千多米的大孤山铁矿，矿<span class=\"vocab\">坑<span class=\"tooltip\">kēng — pit; hole</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">呈<span class=\"tooltip\">呈...形 chéng...xíng — take the shape of</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">倒<span class=\"tooltip\">dào — inverted</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">金字塔<span class=\"tooltip\">jīn zì tǎ — pyramid</span></span>形，一层一层<span class=\"vocab\">螺旋<span class=\"tooltip\">luó xuán — spiral</span></span>向下，深不见底。那些车轮有两个人高的工程车，在坑中吃力地爬坡，看起来像<span class=\"vocab\">火柴盒<span class=\"tooltip\">huǒ chái hé — matchbox</span></span>般<span class=\"vocab\">渺小<span class=\"tooltip\">miǎo xiǎo — tiny; insignificant</span></span>。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN 3-4.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p3_3.jpg", "alt": "大孤山铁矿" }
    },
    {
      "html": "大孤山不是一个偏远的大矿坑，而是一个完整的<span class=\"vocab\">聚落<span class=\"tooltip\">jù luò — settlement</span></span>，是当年围绕着矿区发展起来的城区，慢慢与鞍山市区连成一片。这里大部份的住宅楼都已<span class=\"vocab\">残破<span class=\"tooltip\">cán pò — dilapidated</span></span>老旧，居民也大多<span class=\"vocab\">上了年纪<span class=\"tooltip\">shàng le nián jì — elderly</span></span>。大孤山还有一整片的“红楼”，已经<span class=\"vocab\">人去楼空<span class=\"tooltip\">rén qù lóu kōng — deserted building</span></span>，全部被<span class=\"vocab\">征收<span class=\"tooltip\">zhēng shōu — expropriate</span></span>了。这些红楼在上世纪五十年代建成，供苏联专家居住，也算是比较早期的高级住宅楼。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN 3-5.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p3_4.jpg", "alt": "红楼" }
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍山因有钢而有城，<span class=\"vocab\">严格<span class=\"tooltip\">yán gé — strict</span></span>说起来是座日本人打造起来的城市。如果要<span class=\"vocab\">深入<span class=\"tooltip\">shēn rù — deep; thorough</span></span>讨论东北，日本元素是很难跳过的一<span class=\"vocab\">环<span class=\"tooltip\">huán — one link; one part</span></span>，只不过由于<span class=\"vocab\">众所周知<span class=\"tooltip\">zhòng suǒ zhōu zhī — as everyone knows</span></span>的原因，经常是<span class=\"vocab\">假装<span class=\"tooltip\">jiǎ zhuāng — pretend</span></span>不存在。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN 3-6.mp4"
    },
    {
      "html": "从1918年至1945年，日本从鞍山地区<span class=\"vocab\">掠夺<span class=\"tooltip\">lüè duó — plunder</span></span>钢铁资源超过1000万吨，日本的<span class=\"vocab\">野心<span class=\"tooltip\">yě xīn — ambition</span></span>是要在鞍山建世界最大的钢铁企业，并计划用几十年时间，将鞍山变成伪满的四大都市之一。日本人一边掠夺一边做<span class=\"vocab\">长远<span class=\"tooltip\">cháng yuǎn — long-term</span></span>规画，大概没想到最后都是<span class=\"vocab\">替人做嫁衣<span class=\"tooltip\">tì rén zuò jià yī — to work for others' benefit without reward</span></span>。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN 3-7.mp4",
      "image": { "src": "img/p3_5.jpg", "alt": "昭和制钢所旧影" }
    },
    {
      "html": "鞍山的<span class=\"vocab\">车牌<span class=\"tooltip\">chē pái — license plate</span></span>是“<span class=\"vocab\">辽C<span class=\"tooltip\">liáo C — Liaoning C license plate</span></span>”，也就是辽宁省排在沈阳、大连之后的第三大城市。但我在网上发鞍山照片时，发现不知道鞍山在哪儿的人还真<span class=\"vocab\">不在少数<span class=\"tooltip\">bú zài shǎo shù — quite a number</span></span>。总算是来过一次鞍山了，我觉得这是个很出故事的地方：大量日本影响是故事，全国支援鞍山，鞍山支援全国也是故事，当然<span class=\"vocab\">下岗<span class=\"tooltip\">xià gǎng — to be laid off</span></span><span class=\"vocab\">潮<span class=\"tooltip\">cháo — tide; trend</span></span>也是故事，这些年咖啡店<span class=\"vocab\">遍地开花<span class=\"tooltip\">biàn dì kāi huā — to blossom everywhere</span></span>也是奇妙的故事。",
      "audio": "audio/ANSHAN 3-8.mp4"
    }
  ],
